Name: Two Legs
About the game: Features of the game: You have to jump a lot Shoot your opponents a lot Lifting in up Below you will find red hot spikes moving up It's raining on the level The main character is a frog that can jump, shoot and teleport! Who is the main enemy of the frog? Perch, yes perch! But the perch cannot come to the surface. Dangerous mechanical robots under the control of a perch are placed on the level, and a special danger is coming from below!
